AI Based Travel Planner
Objective:
Design an intelligent travel planner that uses a knowledge base of tourist destinations, attractions, food recommendations and budget information to generate personalized travel plans.

A traveler provides:

Interests
Budget
Duration of stay

The AI system recommends:

Suitable destination
Tourist attractions
Food recommendations
Estimated trip cost
Daily itinerary
Knowledge Base

The system contains information regarding:

Cities:
Jaipur
Goa
Delhi
Kerala
Manali

Attractions:
for eg.
Amber Fort
Hawa Mahal
Baga Beach
India Gate
Solang Valley
Food Recommendations

Examples:
Dal Baati Churma
Fish Curry
Street Food
Kerala Sadya
AI Components Used
Knowledge Representation

Tourism information is represented using structured objects.

Recommendation Engine

Cities are scored based on:

User interests
Budget compatibility
Attraction ratings
Food ratings
Cost Assessment

Total cost includes:

Accommodation
Food
Transportation
Attraction expenses
